#originalStanceText=Yes
#originalTopic=does-owning-a-gun-make-you-safer
As a  handicapped  person ( I am a  BKA Below  the  Knee Amputee ) I am unable  to  flee, or  back up.I  tend  to fall  down whenever  I  try  to  back away.I feel  much  more  secure  when  I am able  to have the  protection of  a  firearm with  me.